00:56:40,226 --> 00:56:44,288
[SPEAKER_00]: At least in my experience, that's been the case.

517
00:56:45,469 --> 00:56:50,451
[SPEAKER_00]: Also not uncommon, most of the issues that were raised were raised by the union.

